HAO Windows notes
=================

The project has been adjusted for a stock Windows build:

1. QtColorWidgets is no longer required.
2. VTK source changes are no longer required.
3. VTK is located through the VTK_ROOT environment variable.

Recommended build flow:

1. Install Qt 6 MinGW 64-bit.
2. Build or install VTK 9.6 with the same MinGW toolchain and Qt support.
3. Set environment variables:

   setx QT_DIR C:\Qt\6.10.1\mingw_64
   setx VTK_ROOT C:\VTK

4. Open a new command prompt.
5. Run check_windows_env.bat.
6. Run build_windows.bat.
7. Run run_windows.bat.

See WINDOWS_RUN_GUIDE.md for details.
